1427
01:24:12.402 --> 01:24:13.886
There's a difference, I guess,

1428
01:24:13.920 --> 01:24:16.544
between being freaked out
by things that you imagine


1429
01:24:16.578 --> 01:24:19.064
and being freaked out by things
