1430
01:24:22.481 --> 01:24:24.931
JAN: This, I have to say,
was the most...


1431
01:24:26.278 --> 01:24:27.727
terrifying experience, but yeah,

1432
01:24:27.762 --> 01:24:29.764
I don't know why I didn't react
