1565
01:31:07.610 --> 01:31:09.508
BRUCE: This is a Blackberry.

1566
01:31:10.785 --> 01:31:13.270
On the back it has the lens.

1567
01:31:13.305 --> 01:31:14.617
It's not like the modern ones.

1568
01:31:14.651 --> 01:31:18.310
It has a camera on the front
