1569
01:31:18.344 --> 01:31:20.208
Though I'd be taking
your picture right now,


1570
01:31:20.243 --> 01:31:22.003
but I would not be
taking my picture.


1571
01:31:22.866 --> 01:31:24.627
Something happened
to the camera.


1572
01:31:24.661 --> 01:31:26.318
